{"tid":815701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人連二等公民都唔係","createTime":"2018-09-12T08:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T04:04:18.000Z","uid":137715,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"30e0b8010199b38584f3e333a157fb95bb8e7ca2","tid":815701,"uid":137715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:39:34.000Z","msg":"香港生活既港豬們<br />\n生活係呢個彈丸之地，每日過住無限既循環，工作工作同工作<br />\n星期六日係唯一可以比我地攤抖下既時間<br />\n但係幾時開始，我地連屋企樓下果條小街橫行都守護唔到？<br />\n以往可以同三五知己飲淡茶既地方都逼滿哂新港人？<br />\n<br />\n既然無辦法去抵擋蟲害，我唯一可以揀既就係逃避<br />\n逃到一個我以爲真正遠離煩囂既地方----大自然<br />\n每次行上山我都好享受，我唔洗再攝手攝腳 避東避西<br />\n每一淡都係最新鮮既空氣<br />\n呢到係一個不論您窮富老幼都會歡迎您既地方<br />\n我唔想無左呢個地方 <br />\n幫幫手 守護返香港剩低「真係」屬於我地既地方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/greenpeacehk/videos/307618146709570/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgreenpeacehk%2Fvideos%2F307618146709570%2F&d=LQWnglECIL2He5N2i7ZqgARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=76ae7d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/greenpeacehk/videos/307618146709570/</a>"},{"pid":"4862c1b1422d6ecf58442448b9dee96a52299409","tid":815701,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;公民&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾多等都唔關香港人事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fda22360f5613f56e671330da9a9e239d0da9f","tid":815701,"uid":178101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:03:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a53c9bd021e94e11c2f7ad3ff3858dc476dba4bd","tid":815701,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"「真正遠離煩囂既地方----大自然」<br />\n睇你去幾山，好多行山徑D 人多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d315e79d736fe2565884fdc838a3319491e22c75","tid":815701,"uid":137715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53c9bd021e94e11c2f7ad3ff38